  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2550707">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2550707/" class="title-link">训诂必读</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2550707"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/14860663/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u14860663-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/14860663/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">李法健</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-10-17"
      class="main-meta">2009-10-17 18:14:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2550707_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       一本不到150頁的小書花了17天讀完，實在算不得快。合上《訓詁學》的一刹那，竟然有些依依不捨，而不是完成任務的解脫與興奮。斷斷續續讀過的訓詁學教材也不少了，郭在貽先生的《訓詁學》卻仍能帶給我無盡的驚喜，一如陸宗達先生的《訓詁簡論》帶給我的感覺。覺得不寫點東...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2550707/#comments">(8回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">28有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2550707_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2550707_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1422834">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1422834/" class="title-link">不通训诂怎么能行？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1422834"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2643954/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2643954-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2643954/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">相忘于江湖</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-06-28"
      class="main-meta">2008-06-28 18:08:11</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1422834_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  号称喜欢国学的人，却不通训诂学，甚至连训诂学都不知道是什么，岂不是天下第一怪事？  这本书和另外一本书可以参考着看——《现代训诂学探论》

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1422834/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
